OL,3,CGregg Wallace announces TikTok 12-hour
OL,4,Clive cooking show
OL,6,FFormer MasterChef presenter Gregg
OL,7,FWallace has announced a 12-hour live
OL,8,Fcooking show to air on his TikTok
OL,9,Faccount.
OL,11,FThe show, titled Gregg's Kitchen, will
OL,12,Ffeature Wallace alongside guests such
OL,13,Fas the proprietors of Wolverhampton-
OL,14,Fbased Malik Butchers, who post content
OL,15,Fon social media.
OL,17,FIt will go live at 10am on Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
