OL,3,CGregg Wallace announces TikTok 12-hour
OL,4,Clive cooking show
OL,6,FWallace was sacked by the BBC last
OL,7,FJuly after an investigation into
OL,8,Fhistorical allegations of misconduct,
OL,9,Fwhich upheld multiple accusations
OL,10,Fagainst him.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
