OL,3,CGregg Wallace announces TikTok 12-hour
OL,4,Clive cooking show
OL,6,FIn a video posted on Malik Butchers's
OL,7,FFacebook page, Wallace says: "We are
OL,8,Fgoing to be cooking some amazing
OL,9,Fdishes, we are going to have some
OL,10,Fincredible guests, lots of cookery,
OL,11,Flots of live chat and more importantly
OL,12,Flots of very good offers for you to
OL,13,Fbuy on TikTok shop."
OL,15,FWallace began co-presenting MasterChef
OL,16,Fin 2005, but it was announced in
OL,17,FNovember 2024 that he would step away
OL,18,Ffrom his role while misconduct
OL,19,Fallegations were investigated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
