OL,3,CGregg Wallace announces TikTok 12-hour
OL,4,Clive cooking show
OL,6,FA review later upheld 45 of the 83
OL,7,Fallegations against him, which mostly
OL,8,Foccurred between 2005 and 2018 and
OL,9,Fincluded one of "unwelcome physical
OL,10,Fcontact".
OL,12,FIt said the "majority of the
OL,13,Fsubstantiated allegations against
OL,14,FWallace related to inappropriate
OL,15,Fsexual language and humour", adding
OL,16,Fthat "a smaller number of allegations
OL,17,Fof other inappropriate language and
OL,18,Fbeing in a state of undress were also
OL,19,Fsubstantiated".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
